snippet.title: Mini Airways Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
An air traffic controller simulator where you command aircraft for takeoff and landing while avoiding crashes!

Play the demo for free on Steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2289650/Mini_Airways/

The full game is expected to launch in July 2024. Don't forget to add us to your wishlist!
